WEBVTT

00:00.016 --> 00:02.617
(Nolan)
Previously on <i>Defiance...</i>

00:02.619 --> 00:06.021
(Irisa) I made a deal with a devil
to save my father.

00:06.056 --> 00:07.890
This devil was a machine,

00:07.924 --> 00:10.826
a ship bent on destroying
the world.

00:10.861 --> 00:13.729
It had big plans for me.

00:15.398 --> 00:19.268
It made me destroy New York City
and hurt the people I love.

00:20.637 --> 00:24.406
What happened?
Did Irisa kill Tommy?

00:24.441 --> 00:26.142
Yes.

00:26.176 --> 00:29.478
You remember Pilar,
Rafe's wife.

00:29.513 --> 00:32.515
You're not still sick?

00:32.549 --> 00:33.682
Never been better.

00:33.717 --> 00:35.484
- [grunts]
- Alak!

00:35.519 --> 00:37.286
[grunts]

00:37.320 --> 00:42.324
And if you struggle,
you'll hurt the baby.

00:42.359 --> 00:44.760
Pilar has kidnapped
Alak and Christie.

00:44.794 --> 00:46.729
Do you know how many people
I have killed?

00:46.763 --> 00:49.031
Do you know how many people
you can still save?

00:49.065 --> 00:50.199
(Irisa)
To save the planet,

00:50.233 --> 00:53.202
we had to travel into the heart
of darkness,

00:53.236 --> 00:56.839
the ship buried
deep under the town of Defiance.

00:59.509 --> 01:00.876
He did it.

01:00.911 --> 01:02.578
Looks like
we just saved the world.

01:02.612 --> 01:04.613
That's it.
All right.

01:04.647 --> 01:07.550
[dramatic music]

01:07.584 --> 01:09.752
♪ ♪

01:09.786 --> 01:12.087
I love you, baby girl.

01:12.122 --> 01:13.756
Any word on Nolan?

01:13.790 --> 01:15.524
(Mercado)
He disappeared.

01:15.559 --> 01:17.726
Old St. Louis is gone.

01:17.761 --> 01:21.230
If Nolan was in the collapse,
I'm afraid he's gone as well.

01:26.482 --> 01:28.065
_

