04:22.112 --> 04:25.547
(Bailey) Madam Mayor,
the stasis nets just went dark.

04:27.050 --> 04:29.151
I ordered them
to pull the plug.

04:29.185 --> 04:30.919
Gulanite reserves
are down to 3%.

04:30.954 --> 04:33.655
City charter stipulates that
all power be diverted to heating

04:33.690 --> 04:35.324
and medical services.

04:35.358 --> 04:38.127
And they're still
asking for you at the NeedWant.

04:38.161 --> 04:41.597
Of course.

04:41.631 --> 04:44.600
With the stasis nets down,
the town is a sitting duck

04:44.634 --> 04:48.036
for raiders or whatever else
comes through Bissel Pass.

04:48.071 --> 04:49.838
You think
I don't know that?

04:49.873 --> 04:51.573
People are scared.

04:51.608 --> 04:54.109
Yeah, well, I'm scared too.

04:54.144 --> 04:56.211
Don't tell anybody that.

05:02.752 --> 05:05.721
- [tense music]
- _

