05:42.659 --> 05:45.661
[orbs buzzing]

05:59.342 --> 06:02.244
[pop music on record player]

06:02.278 --> 06:10.185
♪ ♪

06:11.788 --> 06:13.755
Better be an emergency,
Lambert.

06:13.790 --> 06:15.791
I've got a town to run.

06:15.825 --> 06:17.693
(Lambert) But it's Doc Yewll.
She's up 30K.

06:17.727 --> 06:19.261
Yewll?
She's not a gambler.

06:19.295 --> 06:20.662
What's she up to?

06:20.697 --> 06:22.831
I don't know, but if she
keeps going, you know,

06:22.866 --> 06:24.700
she's gonna clean us out.

06:24.734 --> 06:26.268
Doc Yewll.

06:26.302 --> 06:29.238
You don't normally gamble
in my establishment.

06:29.272 --> 06:30.372
Just cutting loose.

06:30.406 --> 06:32.774
Getting my ya-ya's out.

06:32.809 --> 06:34.510
Winning big, I see.

06:34.544 --> 06:37.312
Yeah.
You angling for a tip?

06:37.347 --> 06:38.647
Here you go, legs.

06:38.681 --> 06:40.983
- Now scoot.
- [gunshot]

06:41.017 --> 06:43.585
- Everybody stay calm!
- Nobody move.

06:43.620 --> 06:45.954
(man) Hand over your cash,
scrip chips, and jewelry.

06:45.989 --> 06:48.156
Don't you move.

06:48.191 --> 06:51.159
(man) Everyone does as they're told,
and everyone walks away.

06:51.194 --> 06:52.895
- Empty your pockets.
- Don't even think about it.

06:52.929 --> 06:56.331
(man)
Empty 'em!

06:56.366 --> 07:00.369
Turn around!

07:00.403 --> 07:01.770
Move it!

07:01.804 --> 07:03.939
- Ah! I don't think so!
- [grunts]

07:03.973 --> 07:06.542
Get that safe open!

07:06.576 --> 07:09.711
Friend, I don't run
this place anymore.

07:09.746 --> 07:11.146
You're still the owner!

07:11.180 --> 07:14.082
But I don't know
the combination.

07:14.117 --> 07:15.751
[gunshot]

07:15.785 --> 07:19.621
Next shot
goes through someone's skull.

07:19.656 --> 07:22.624
Okay.

07:22.659 --> 07:24.960
Okay.

07:32.101 --> 07:33.902
Let me guess.

07:33.937 --> 07:37.773
You're an out-of-work miner.

07:37.807 --> 07:39.341
Hap, is that you
under that mask?

07:39.375 --> 07:41.076
Just get the scrip!

07:41.110 --> 07:44.313
Things feel pretty desperate
around here, don't they?

07:44.347 --> 07:45.714
Mines collapsed.

07:45.748 --> 07:48.984
Pow farms covered
under a ton of snow.

07:49.018 --> 07:51.587
Construction jobs nonexistent.
But this?

07:51.621 --> 07:53.188
This is not the answer.

07:53.222 --> 07:55.691
Shut up,
and give me the <i>jekking</i> cash!

07:55.725 --> 07:57.025
[thud]

07:57.060 --> 07:58.460
Berlin, look out!

07:58.494 --> 07:59.494
[gunshot]

08:01.998 --> 08:03.865
[grunting]

08:03.900 --> 08:08.170
- [gunshots]
- Ahh! Ahh!

08:08.204 --> 08:09.871
You okay?

08:09.906 --> 08:10.939
It's been a day.

08:10.974 --> 08:11.974
[groans]

08:19.380 --> 08:24.420
_

08:25.800 --> 08:27.844
_

